QuestData.Title: Vinyl: Battle of Gnomeregan
QuestData.Description:
<This pressed vinyl is surprisingly still intact. Its label says it contains the recording of a song called "Battle of Gnomeragan."
You should be able to install this vinyl into the gramophone back in Rustbolt.>
